The problem of inferring information about a user query using only visible information and constraints involves reasoning and inference, which are key topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the complexity of the problem, which is related to logic and complexity theory (cs.LO). The presence of integrity constraints also suggests a potential connection to cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the problem of inferring information from partial information is a common theme in data science (cs.DS).
